import React from 'react'
import {
    SimpleGrid,
    Box,
    Text
} from '@chakra-ui/react'
import social_media from '../data_1'

function DashboardMain(){

    return (
        <>
            <SimpleGrid columns={4} spacing={10}>
                {
                    social_media.map((sm) =>{
                        <Box
                        display='flex'
                        flexDirection='column'
                        justifyContent='center'
                        alignItems="center"
                        borderTop="5px solid hsl(208, 92%, 53%)"
                        h='180px'
                        bgColor='gray.200'>
                            <Text
                            mb={2}>
                                Hola 1
                                </Text>
                            <Text
                            mb={2}>
                                Hola 2
                            </Text>
                            <Text
                            mb={2}>
                                Hola 3
                            </Text>
                            <Text
                            mb={2}>
                                Hola 4
                            </Text>
                        </Box>
                    })
                }
                
            </SimpleGrid>
        </>
    )
}

export default DashboardMain
